import { useState } from "react"; const Form = ()=>{ const [form, setForm] = useState({ Nombre:"", Imagen:"", Vida:"", Ataque:"", Defensa:"", Velocidad:"", Altura:"", Peso:"", tipo:[] }) const changeHandler = (event)=>{ const property = event.target.name; const value = event.target.value; setForm({...form,[property]:value}) } return(
) } export default Form;
